frontmatter.title: Introducing The Hackathon Society Blog
frontmatter.excerpt: The word Hackathon has been largely associated with Computers and coding for a long time and we at Hackathon Society want to break that stigma by organizing hackathons which do not require an individual to have any programming knowledge.

frontmatter.title: Introduction to Artificial Neural Network
frontmatter.excerpt: The term Neural Network has been used as a buzzword a lot more than anything else in the world of Computer Science, especially during the last couple decades. What exactly is it?
